    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "The hero needs to gather ingredients for their potions. Use a loop to gather a specific number of ingredients, and show progress with a counter. \r\n## Do This: \r\n- Run the code to see how ingredients are collected.\r\n- Modify the code to collect 12 ingredients instead of 5.",
